com.ptc.jws.servlet.data

Interface IeElementBasedBean


  • public interface IeElementBasedBean
    An interface beans can implement to streamline Element to bean and bean to Element translation. Server side beans or JAXB objects may choose to implement this interface to translate Info*Engine data to/from XML.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      The bean should populate its members from the supplied Element.
